---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="What data this site collects, where it goes, and how to request its deletion. A short, honest disclosure."
>
  <Section eyebrow="Privacy Policy">
    <h1 slot="heading">What this site collects, and where it goes</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        This is a small advisory practice website. The technical footprint is
        deliberately minimal: there's no advertising network, no user tracking,
        no behavioural analytics, no cookies set for marketing purposes. This
        page exists to make the small data flows that do happen visible and to
        explain what you can do about them.
      </p>

      <h2>What's collected when</h2>

      <p>
        <strong>When you submit the contact form:</strong> Your name, email
        address, and message are sent to Formspree (a form-handling service
        operated by Formspree Inc., based in the United States), which delivers
        the submission as an email to Argo. Formspree may set a short-lived
        session cookie in your browser during the submission process. The
        submitted message is retained by Formspree according to their data
        retention policy and forwarded as email; no copy is stored on this
        website's servers.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>When you visit any page:</strong> Cloudflare Web Analytics
        records anonymised visit data (page URL, referrer, country-level
        geography derived from IP address, browser and device type) for the
        purpose of helping us understand which pages get read and where visitors
        come from. Cloudflare Web Analytics does not set tracking cookies, does
        not record individual visitor identity, and does not combine your visits
        across sessions into a profile. IP addresses are processed for the
        analytics computation but are not stored alongside the analytics data.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>When you click an external link</strong> (for example, to a
        sales deck on Google Drive or to LinkedIn): you leave this site and
        become subject to the privacy policy of whatever service the link points
        to. We do not track outbound clicks.
      </p>

      <p>
        That's the whole list. No other data is collected, set, stored, or
        transmitted by this site.
      </p>

      <h2>What we don't do</h2>

      <ul>
        <li>We don't use Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, LinkedIn Insight Tag, or any other behavioural tracking service.</li>
        <li>We don't sell, share, or rent data to third parties.</li>
        <li>We don't display advertising.</li>
        <li>We don't profile visitors or build audience segments.</li>
        <li>We don't use cookies to remember preferences or track sessions across visits, beyond Formspree's short-lived form-submission cookie noted above.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Your rights</h2>

      <p>
        Under the EU General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and Estonian
        privacy law (Isikuandmete kaitse seadus), you have the right to:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Request a copy of any personal data this site or its service providers (Formspree, Cloudflare) hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
        <li>Lodge a complaint with the Estonian Data Protection Inspectorate (Andmekaitse Inspektsioon) if you believe your data has been processed in violation of GDPR</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, write to
        <a href="mailto:argo@rannamets.ee">argo@rannamets.ee</a>. Requests
        typically take a few business days; we'll route the request to Formspree
        or Cloudflare as needed and confirm completion in writing.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>

      <p>
        This site is operated by Magere OÜ, a private Estonian company. The data
        controller for the purposes of GDPR is Argo Rannamets, principal of
        Magere OÜ.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:argo@rannamets.ee">argo@rannamets.ee</a></li>
        <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+3725110241">+372 511 0241</a></li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        For questions about this policy or about your data, contact us at the
        email above.
      </p>

      <h2>When this policy was last updated</h2>

      <p>
        This policy was published on June 9, 2026. Material changes to the
        policy will be reflected by updating this date.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Base>
